Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:46.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}森の奥　神様さえ知らない場所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:52.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}実った果実を巡る物語
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:58.15,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}裸足で彷徨う　少女たちの影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.19,0:22:06.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4}純粋で　愚か　どこに辿り着くのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:21.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}孤独になるために出会うわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:27.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}その優しさが嘘ならばいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.19,0:22:33.74,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}壊れた胸の扉　もう触れたりしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:38.84,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}きっと戻れなくなるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:47.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}望まないはずなのに　信じては傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.41,0:22:50.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}怖れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.42,0:22:57.37,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}真っ白に汚れた天使の羽根で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:23:02.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}私はエデンの道を辿る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:09.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}もう少し世界が穏やかだったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:17.91,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4}みんな　幸せになれたかもね　永遠に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:46.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}森林深處  連神都不曾知曉的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:52.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}譜寫著圍繞成熟果實的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:58.15,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}赤足彷徨其中的少女們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.19,0:22:06.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4}純粹而愚笨的身影  走向的是未知的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:21.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}邂逅的目的並非尋求孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:27.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多希望那份溫柔會是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.19,0:22:33.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}遍體鱗傷的心靈  不想再讓任何人觸碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:38.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}因為再也回不到從前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:47.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不再抱有任何期待  信任只會帶來傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.41,0:22:50.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}讓人膽顫心驚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.42,0:22:57.37,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}天使被玷污的純白羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:23:02.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}指引我追尋著伊甸園的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:09.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}世界若是能再風平浪靜一些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:17.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4}也許大家便能獲得永遠的幸福
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TXT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你能躲掉剛剛這下？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的周圍  時間的流速是正常的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢耍我  不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.10,0:00:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你對蓄意殺傷同學這事就這麼無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事實上沒插中  所以我無罪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這女人的六法全書裡似乎沒有殺人未遂這一項
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二你才剛來就攤上了一樁倒霉事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:00:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然對我無害  不過影響心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你太急著想和她交好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,靠近她的時候你沒察覺到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她周圍的防壁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這遲鈍總有一天會要你命的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是事關性命我也會變得敏銳起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我不覺得這能危及性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這態度怎麼去談場普通的戀愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.72,0:01:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,師父也教訓過我這些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,師父？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看書要在明亮的地方看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我師父的教誨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可這天氣真是熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有脈搏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來不是毒蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挺涼快的啊  這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃吧  多吃點養肥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是想養肥了吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小農蝦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小農蝦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小農蝦  再過來點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你可別掉池裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真輕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你體重連40公斤都沒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放人家下來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用不著客氣  我只是盡我所能而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你要躲著我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你記得我的名字嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風見…雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  叫雄二就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直呼名字太讓人害羞了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你想怎麼叫就怎麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  那就…哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥…好吧  隨你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蒔菜  剛才我看到你口袋裡放有醋醃魷魚對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害  釣到小農蝦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是小農蝦  是小龍蝦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小農蝦好紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,估計是這池子裡面水草豐富吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飼料豐富的話  小龍蝦就會變得很紅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是飼料少的話會變怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,變青
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,變青？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一直給剛出生的小龍蝦餵食不含胡蘿蔔素的飼料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一個月左右就會變青
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前在書上看到後  做過實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好  我也想做實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就放了牠  然後自己釣個試試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你今天跟我一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我釣的這個小農蝦…不對  是小龍蝦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想拿回去做實驗看看會不會真的變青
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飼料要餵不含胡蘿蔔素的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝…嗎  還真是個奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您當真不是開玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然要讓男生來這個如同女校的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您是想讓我們全給他強姦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次入學的男生絕對不會做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這點我可以保證
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}（蛇行蛇道）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那天後我就開始請假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用盡一切手段收集那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs33}以上就是現在所了解到的全部情況。\N若能提供有關風見雄二的過去的有用情報，\N我將獻上懸賞金100萬日元。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風見雄二的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  我調查得越深情報就越錯綜複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像有什麼人在搗亂一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我用盡一切手段都收集不到確切情報的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能是個正常人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風見雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  絕不會認同你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看著就像在套招演練一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能別再搞這種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那眼神是要幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滿滿肯定會遭到鮮血報復的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你別嚇我啦蒔菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,期待個屁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定是害怕你入侵她的私人空間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  榊同學是這學校創建時就入學的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止這裡都是她能掌握的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是突然來了個異性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還是查不出底細的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她就想將你除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  解決方法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種煩惱也包含在學生生活內吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真會矇人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  習慣普通的學生生活了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是假扮學生做密探工作一般沒法放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你過得挺開心的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我承認過得確實挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是看到玻璃上映出自己的笑臉時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我覺得毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像不是我自己一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有一種不協調感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有著「笑什麼笑  你誰啊」的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後突然就笑不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢就會習慣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那幾個孩子剛來學校的時候也都跟你說過同樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然來到這裡的其他人也都各有隱情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學生們都是抱有各自的問題而入學到這學校來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有些學生是不願意自己的隱私被別人觸及
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有些是問題一旦暴露便會影響到她們的正常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比如  像你這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴說慢慢就會習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可習慣了又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如今不論我做出什麼改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失去的東西也回不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你找我有事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我講點故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,講故事？  講故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要聽什麼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天太熱了  講點能讓人涼快的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涼快的故事啊  我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我在以前的學校從學長那裡聽來的故事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難以置信  你們什麼時候交情變這麼好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隨其自然而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你能像這樣跟榊同學也變好點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說我也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是那傢伙單方面拒絕我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她本性也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前學校跟本地的人起糾紛時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是她帶頭做義務勞動緩和的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的人你認識嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}你好 　      　{\r}\NHowdy  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她都叫出你名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙搞什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音  你帶蒔菜先走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  學生生活過得還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的  你來幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是這麼冷漠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是來看看你能不能在普通學校裡過普通生活而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前為止沒有任何問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若非要追究的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣來找我就是唯一的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是幫你偽造好毫無破綻的經歷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想說太多謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顏色和說謊都是疊得越多就越黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說謊是會變紅才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:14:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色疊多了也會變黑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就機靈點別造成這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不想……意外死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才希望你別做這種我預料之外的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我就先回去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的只是來看看我過得怎樣而已嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一開始就說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是關於工作的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定會先電話聯繫你再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你來這城市的時候是步行走過縣境線的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明都給你買好電車的票了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭電車  你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可哪有人會因為討厭電車就步行200公里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此還被警察帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被上頭數落的可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你能不能別用「這女人真麻煩啊」的眼神盯著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:15:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你會超能力嗎  為什麼會知道我在想什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我哭給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  JB
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知錯就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  有空再聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(536,660)}Julia Bardera
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉婭·巴爾德拉  一般稱其JB
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟她自己所說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是個麻煩的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來  該怎麼跟天音她們解釋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  剛才那金髮女是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:16:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的監護人兼打工那邊的上司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二你還去打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打什麼工？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不太好解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是打掃垃圾  潛入各種地方做清掃活動的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的髒活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那那個金髮女也是清掃業的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過她是下命令的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會親自去做髒活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,問題問完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,問完了就回自己座位去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蒔菜  今天的作業你做完了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}要被罵啦  我感覺要被罵啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}幸  借我抄一下  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最關鍵的地方你還沒說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  這麼鄭重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟那人的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是情侶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為你想說什麼呢  無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這對我來說很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得像我這樣的男人會有戀人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為是像你這樣的男人所以才看不出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你來這學校前都在幹些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來這裡前啊  在當小白臉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小白臉？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,靠沒血緣關係的女人吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人就是剛才的金髮女？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  她是那女人的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人死了後才到她照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真不要臉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代價就是替她做牛做馬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我問心無愧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  你還沒有戀人對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:17:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  看什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你都聽到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我對你可是一點興趣都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別  別擅自讓我聽這種奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傲嬌得很好  滿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你還嘲笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人都還沒回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  因為事發突然所以沒能留手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美子  我不是你的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會傷害由美子  我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你別再做這種多餘的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是在說謊你好好觀察查證
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要用刀除掉我等你查證後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一個問題想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除了弱點之外我都可以回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那還真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天我會查出你的弱點的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好加油吧  由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你能不能別這麼自然的直呼我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你連我姓名都沒叫過一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有臉來要求我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可也不至於突然直呼名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  那就是說我們可以用姓稱呼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我為什麼要跟你用同等地位的稱呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交朋友就該從這種地方開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們起個好玩的外號怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來外號對我們來說還有點早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才提議用姓氏稱呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教  風見同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  請多指教  榊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的學生  能打擾下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝禮？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了你們  城裡變得乾淨多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,替我跟你的朋友們也道聲謝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子們是你的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂由美子  你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點我們就不等你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交朋友就該從這種地方開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊同學  趕緊起床
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不妙了  有個暴走族闖到我們美濱學園來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是從今天開始到這學校就讀的周防天音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以後請多指教  榊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫松島滿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:22:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我才不是為了你們才轉學到這來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我叫入巢蒔菜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是今天轉學到這學校預讀班的小嶺幸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.41,0:22:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們給我跪下舔鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.82,0:23:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然您叫我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說又有轉學生要來了對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  預計明年春天就轉學進來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的轉學生是個男生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  甜食生活
